</div></div></div><div id="a192368d2d18007b66ea6c7920896b71" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192368d2d1900afd2166c454ca09d9f" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192368ddc4f00b578ce9d55b6c65966" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom24">Add your product description that will be useful for your customers. Add</p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#0abda0;">"Make A Stride"</span> is built on a foundation of excellence, innovation, and a passion for driving transformative change. </span></span></strong></p>

<p> </p>

<p><span style="color:#0abda0;"><strong><span style="font-size:18px;">Meet our Leader:</span></strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">A dynamic, results-oriented Business Strategy and Technology Executive, she brings over 25 years of industry experience. With pivotal roles at renowned organizations like NASA, eBay, and Pelco by Schneider Electric, as well as various startups, her wealth of expertise fuels our mission: Aspire, Assess, Act, and Achieve!</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#0abda0;"><strong><span style="font-size:18px;">Her Commitment:</span></strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">She is dedicated to helping organizations assess their potential, take decisive action, and achieve lasting success. Her work empowers businesses to navigate the digital landscape with confidence and make a significant impact.  Her leadership style is focused on delivering value and building resilience in the face of technological evolutions.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#0abda0;"><strong><span style="font-size:18px;">Notable Achievements:</span></strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">She has been honored with the "President's Award for Corporate Excellence" for creating an application that enables insurance agents to effectively track their work. She also received NASA's Achievement Award for 2 consecutive years for her contributions to the team responsible for the development, evaluation, and implementation of a cutting-edge cloud computing capability (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS), known as Nebula (now OpenStack), to support NASA missions. <a data-_="Link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nebula_(computing_platform)" target="_blank" title="NASA Nebula Team Wiki">Wikipedia link</a> and a picture of the <a data-_="Link" href="javascript:void(0);" data-popup="wb_popup:Nebula-Team/?wbPopupMode=1;w=400;h=320;pagePopup=1;" title="Nebula Team">Nebula team</a>. Reference to this project at <a data-_="Link" href="https://www.nasa.gov/image-article/openstack-cloud-computing-platform/" target="_blank">NASA site</a> and a <a data-_="Link" href="https://ntrs.nasa.gov/api/citations/20120011651/downloads/20120011651.pdf" target="_blank">presentation</a> by the CIO, James F. Williams</span></span></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#0abda0;"><strong><span style="font-size:18px;">A Seasoned Technology Executive:</span></strong></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">She brings a strategic mindset adept at establishing, expanding, and fortifying product presence in complex technical landscapes. Known for her ability to assess organizational needs and steer advanced software solutions, her expertise spans Development, Quality Engineering, DevSecOps, Agile Technical Management, Product, Program Management, Technical Project Management, Customer Support, and Strategy.  Her experience encompasses adaptive change in startups, M&amp;A integrations, and digital transformations.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-size:18px;">Her leadership has driven technology innovation and shaped strategic directions, optimizing performance, while achieving business objectives.  She has a proven track record in building, nurturing, and managing global teams, consistently exceeding expectations.</span></span></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>
</div></div></div><div id="a192368d2d190122f73eef1f094fc118" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192368ea86d009f36b2d6ea111fab7d" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color:#0abda0"><strong><span style="font-size:18px">Skillsets &amp; Recent Accomplishments:</span></strong></span></p>

<p class="wb-stl-normal" style="text-align: justify;"> </p>
</div><div id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42" class="wb_element wb-accordion" data-plugin="Accordion"><div class="wb-accordion-type-accordion"><div class="panel-group" id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-list"><div class="panel panel-default " data-item-id="0"><div class="panel-heading" id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading0"><div class="panel-title left"><a class="wb-accordion-title collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-list" href="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-0" expanded="true" aria-controls="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-0" onclick="var $this=$(this);$this.parents('.panel-group').find('.panel').removeClass('in');$this.hasClass('collapsed') &amp;&amp; $this.parents('.panel').addClass('in');"><div>➢ People, Practice/Process &amp; Technology</div><span class="glyphicon pull-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="panel-collapse collapse " id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading0"><div class="panel-body"><div id="a19236910f4a016a0d219ba34f8951fb" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19236910f4a02c5cac2201a189e0e54" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><ul>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She developed and executed a three-pronged strategy—People, Practice/Process, and Technology—to create a scalable platform while optimizing costs through strategic investments and efficiency improvements.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She leveraged cutting-edge technology and optimized team structures to streamline operations, enhancing overall productivity and reducing operational bottlenecks.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She mentored and led both local and remote teams, fostering collaboration and cultivating a high-performance culture with a blended leadership style, significantly improving time-to-market.</li>
</ul>
</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default " data-item-id="1"><div class="panel-heading" id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading1"><div class="panel-title left"><a class="wb-accordion-title collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-list" href="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-1" expanded="true" aria-controls="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-1" onclick="var $this=$(this);$this.parents('.panel-group').find('.panel').removeClass('in');$this.hasClass('collapsed') &amp;&amp; $this.parents('.panel').addClass('in');"><div>➢ Agile Transformation</div><span class="glyphicon pull-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="panel-collapse collapse " id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading1"><div class="panel-body"><div id="a19236910f4a0327f7efd1ad2f5c5e0d" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19236910f4a0495659daa4f19b1e0af" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;"><em><u><strong>High-Performance with Quality:</strong></u></em> </p>

<ul>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She implemented Agile Scrum, Kanban, and Scrumban methodologies as a Certified Scrum Master, reducing resource utilization by 33% and lowering bug rates by 69%, leading to a 20% increase in customer retention and a 5% revenue uplift within a year.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She restructured teams and enhanced SDLC processes, achieving a 60% cost reduction while improving operational efficiency and delivery timelines.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She provided mentorship that resulted in a 63% decrease in hotfixes and fostered stronger team collaboration across cross-functional teams.</li>
</ul>
</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel panel-default " data-item-id="2"><div class="panel-heading" id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading2"><div class="panel-title left"><a class="wb-accordion-title collapsed" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-list" href="#a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-2" expanded="true" aria-controls="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-2" onclick="var $this=$(this);$this.parents('.panel-group').find('.panel').removeClass('in');$this.hasClass('collapsed') &amp;&amp; $this.parents('.panel').addClass('in');"><div>➢ Digital Transformation</div><span class="glyphicon pull-right"></span></a></div></div><div class="panel-collapse collapse " id="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="a19236910f4a00a1f8171bfe3a0b0d42-item-heading2"><div class="panel-body"><div id="a1923695249600817cdbfb9971605d41" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a1923695249c008dc80bd36f1fd8403a" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom19"><span style="color:#0c7463;"><em><u><strong>Executive Decision Making:</strong></u></em> </span></p>

<ul>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She served as a trusted advisor to C-suite leaders on product, cloud, and tech stack strategies, reducing redundant products by 30% for a more efficient portfolio.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She leveraged executive communication skills to synthesize diverse perspectives into actionable plans, driving company-wide success.</li>
</ul>

<p class="wb-stl-custom19"><span style="color:#0c7463;"><em><u><strong>Data Center, Cloud Infrastructure &amp; AI:</strong></u></em> </span></p>

<ul>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="wb-stl-custom19">She led AWS migration using a lift-and-shift model, formulated a Cloud and AI strategy, and delivered a scalable hybrid SaaS solution with Microservice Architecture, cutting AWS costs by 50%.</p>
</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">
<p class="wb-stl-custom19">She achieved a 15% reduction in downtime and improved disaster recovery by deploying a multi-cloud environment.</p>
</li>
</ul>

<p class="wb-stl-custom19"><span style="color:#0c7463;"><em><u><strong>DevSecOps Culture: </strong></u></em></span></p>

<ul>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She spearheaded the adoption of a DevSecOps culture, integrating security into every phase of the development lifecycle, ensuring early detection and mitigation of risks.</li>
<li class="wb-stl-custom19" style="text-align: justify;">She implemented CI/CD pipelines and automated testing processes, accelerating speed-to-market and reducing bug rates by 69%, significantly improving product quality.</li>
</ul>
